Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.49,0:00:15.50,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Agora eu não consigo me mover... Esse é o meu destino, mas...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.50,0:00:20.58,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Eu não vou desistir mais porque eu despertei.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.58,0:00:25.67,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Meu coração ardente e pulsante reflete a era...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.67,0:00:30.72,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Tem a cor de chamas vivamente em brasa...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.72,0:00:35.68,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Chorando, embora eu não possa ver agora...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.68,0:00:40.23,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Buscando, um marco flutua à frente.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.03,0:00:53.32,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Lá, vou tirar o que resta da minha juventude,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.05,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Se estes lábios secos ficarem úmidos,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.55,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Além do tempo, rumo a uma era apaixonada,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.55,0:01:16.26,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Porque eu acredito que vai se mover...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.49,0:00:15.50,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Embora não possa mudar agora seja o destino,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.50,0:00:20.58,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Pois já despertei e não vou desistir.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.58,0:00:25.67,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}A empolgação ardente reflete a época,
